♪ Come on. rise and march ahead ♪

246
00:18:42.708 --> 00:18:45.666
♪ Like a raging tide without limits ♪

247
00:18:46.375 --> 00:18:48.083
♪ Like the surge that makes you leap ♪

248
00:18:48.166 --> 00:18:49.958
