to earn sympathy votes.

534
00:38:22.625 --> 00:38:25.083
Those eyes that need no kohl.

535
00:38:27.458 --> 00:38:30.375
A nose that needs no adornment.

536
00:38:30.458 --> 00:38:32.833
A rare beauty.

537
00:38:33.291 --> 00:38:35.875
