737
00:55:39.500 --> 00:55:42.666
Hindu Kesari. Coach Mr. Gournaidu.

738
00:55:42.750 --> 00:55:45.458
Welcome! A warm welcome!

739
00:55:46.500 --> 00:55:48.875
In honor of Kodi Rammurthy Naidu.

740
00:55:48.958 --> 00:55:50.833
